649
00:22:00,599 --> 00:22:01,440
Kong Xiaocan, are you leaving or not?

650
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:02,119
Your brother keeps crying!

651
00:22:02,119 --> 00:22:03,319
You won't comfort him, so get out!

652
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:07,759
Twenty-five years in exchange for this?

653
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:08,839
No way.

654
00:22:10,799 --> 00:22:11,319
No way, no way.

655
00:22:19,839 --> 00:22:20,240
