674
00:22:49,680 --> 00:22:51,000
It's not like we can't survive.

675
00:22:51,119 --> 00:22:52,480
But we literally can't survive!

676
00:22:53,359 --> 00:22:54,880
If worse comes to worst, I'll do a work-study program.

677
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,680
You're full of... You can work?

678
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:59,079
When the time comes, the two of us,

679
00:22:59,519 --> 00:23:01,400
