768
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:57,440
You're a good kid.

769
00:25:57,559 --> 00:25:58,920
Yeah, this... this Zhang Chi is actually pretty good.

770
00:26:00,519 --> 00:26:01,000
Heroine.

771
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:02,640
Heroine, what's your name?

772
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:05,519
This...

773
