Mom, Mom, Mom

849
00:28:36,599 --> 00:28:37,119
Go, go

850
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:42,920
Did you pedal? Push!

851
00:28:44,119 --> 00:28:45,160
Push!

852
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:46,839
I'm pushing hard! Keep it down

853
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:48,200
Hurry up

854
00:28:48,279 --> 00:28:49,400
Did you pedal?

855
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:51,519
Did you pedal? Push!

856
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:54,319
Put some effort into it! Push!

857
00:29:12,279 --> 00:29:12,640
Mom

858
00:29:13,119 --> 00:29:13,759
Go to school

859
00:29:14,519 --> 00:29:15,000
What?

860
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:16,640
I said,

861
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:17,960
go to school

862
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:06,839
Why did you bring me here?

863
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:08,200
To start from the top.

864
00:30:11,519 --> 00:30:12,160
Hello there.

865
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:15,480
How would you like it cut?

866
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:16,559
Sir.

867
00:30:16,599 --> 00:30:17,599
Could you just make it...

868
00:30:17,799 --> 00:30:18,960
as chic and pretty as possible.

869
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:19,799
Style it for her.

870
00:30:19,839 --> 00:30:21,039
Let me think.

871
00:30:21,119 --> 00:30:21,599
The main thing is...

872
00:30:21,599 --> 00:30:22,839
she doesn't usually style her hair.

873
00:30:22,839 --> 00:30:24,799
She's never had styling or a hairdo.

874
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:25,359
Anyway, just...

875
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:27,039
see if you can give her big waves.

876
00:30:27,079 --> 00:30:27,960
Right, Tony?

877
00:30:28,319 --> 00:30:29,599
You don't need to dye it.

878
00:30:29,599 --> 00:30:30,720
What about those big curls?

879
00:30:30,799 --> 00:30:31,359
Let me look it up.

880
00:30:31,519 --> 00:30:32,160
Take a look.

881
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:34,440
Is that a no?

882
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:35,640
Is that a no, Tony?

883
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:36,200
I can do it.

884
00:30:36,319 --> 00:30:37,000
Call me Kevin.

885
00:30:37,119 --> 00:30:37,839
Sorry, Kevin.

886
00:30:38,160 --> 00:30:39,400
Just make it temporary.

887
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:41,039
But don't give her auntie curls.

888
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:42,240
My son is right.

889
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:44,200
Live in the moment.

890
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,400
It's time to think about myself.

891
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,720
It's just going to school.

892
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:50,319
It's just restarting a life.

893
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,480
Let's start from the top.

894
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:56,319
Look at you.

895
00:31:57,559 --> 00:31:59,079
You went from Xianghe

896
00:31:59,079 --> 00:32:00,599
straight to the Champs-Élysées.

897
00:32:01,079 --> 00:32:02,119
How is it, son?

898
00:32:02,359 --> 00:32:03,279
It's amazing.

899
00:32:03,279 --> 00:32:04,720
My cousin's fashion sense...

900
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:07,240
I'm your mother.

901
00:32:07,759 --> 00:32:08,359
Okay, okay, okay.

902
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,440
It looks really good.

903
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:21,759
Nineteen years old.

904
00:32:22,759 --> 00:32:24,440
Usually a quarter of one's life.

905
00:32:25,519 --> 00:32:26,480
Or a fifth.

906
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:30,599
We always make life's most important decisions

907
00:32:31,759 --> 00:32:33,759
at our most immature age.

908
00:32:35,599 --> 00:32:36,119
Like me,

909
00:32:37,119 --> 00:32:37,799
Kong Xiaocan.

910
00:32:39,279 --> 00:32:40,279
Just starting my freshman year,

911
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:42,440
I skipped school to go to a snow mountain without telling Mom.

912
00:32:43,559 --> 00:32:45,440
After learning Mom had a terminal illness,

913
00:32:46,559 --> 00:32:48,400
I shed tears of sincere regret.

914
00:32:49,319 --> 00:32:50,960
Then I made a deal with an alien being,

915
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:53,079
trading twenty-five years of my life

916
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:54,480
to give to Mom.

917
00:32:55,759 --> 00:32:56,960
Letting her regain her health

918
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:58,640
and return to her youth.

919
00:33:00,319 --> 00:33:01,079
And now,

920
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:03,119
I'm keeping another secret from her.

921
00:33:03,519 --> 00:33:04,960
Using the last of our family savings,

922
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:07,119
I signed her up for a cram school.

923
00:33:07,119 --> 00:33:08,519
The very last sprint class,

924
00:33:09,079 --> 00:33:10,680
to fulfill her dream of going to college.

925
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:12,400
From now on,

926
00:33:13,039 --> 00:33:14,680
I will shoulder the burden of our little family.

927
00:33:15,279 --> 00:33:15,799
At least,

928
00:33:16,599 --> 00:33:18,279
regarding Mom restarting her life...

929
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:19,480
I want to sign up.

930
00:33:19,799 --> 00:33:20,559
I have no regrets.

931
00:33:23,759 --> 00:33:24,400
I've thought it through.

932
00:33:25,519 --> 00:33:26,400
My goal

933
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,559
is to get into Duxing University.

934
00:33:29,759 --> 00:33:31,559
That way I can go to school with you.

935
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:33,880
No...

936
00:33:34,759 --> 00:33:35,200
How about that?

937
00:33:35,599 --> 00:33:36,160
Happy?

938
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,319
Go over there to pick up materials.

939
00:33:39,759 --> 00:33:40,079
Okay.

940
00:33:41,759 --> 00:33:44,279
Why do you have to cling to me even for college?

941
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:55,319
If we were to select

942
00:33:55,319 --> 00:33:57,000
a ranking of filial sons in this world,

943
00:33:59,279 --> 00:34:00,640
he would certainly be at the top.

944
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:06,920
This handsome man is named Kong Xiaocan.

945
00:34:07,759 --> 00:34:09,079
He is an ordinary son,

946
00:34:10,239 --> 00:34:12,280
but also a young man with a heart full of great love.

947
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:16,679
Who says the heart of a blade of grass

948
00:34:17,119 --> 00:34:18,320
can repay the warmth of the spring sun?

949
00:34:20,239 --> 00:34:22,800
Countless poems praise a mother's dedication to her child.

950
00:34:24,239 --> 00:34:25,480
But even the most flowery language

951
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:26,920
would struggle to describe

952
00:34:27,519 --> 00:34:29,519
this young man's dedication to his mother.

953
00:34:30,679 --> 00:34:32,639
He gave up a colorful future,

954
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:35,559
but gained endless glory.

955
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:45,519
Xiaocan.

956
00:34:50,079 --> 00:34:50,639
What are you watching?

957
00:34:51,559 --> 00:34:52,199
Just looking around.

958
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:02,760
At your age,

959
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:05,639
don't look at this nonsense.

960
00:35:06,159 --> 00:35:06,800
What nonsense am I looking at?

961
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:07,519
What's wrong with watching this?

962
00:35:07,519 --> 00:35:08,639
Why can't I watch this?

963
00:35:10,239 --> 00:35:11,199
Lots of people watch it.

964
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:12,679
It's... it's bad for your health.

965
00:35:14,039 --> 00:35:15,079
Don't be like those people.

966
00:35:16,559 --> 00:35:17,599
Drink... drink your milk.

967
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,960
Watching comedy shows is bad for your health.

968
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,400
Where did you hear that?

969
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:42,599
Xu Rui

970
00:35:44,840 --> 00:35:45,679
When you see

971
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,679
this video,

972
00:35:48,719 --> 00:35:49,159
I

973
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:50,880
will be gone.

974
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:53,400
They say

975
00:35:54,239 --> 00:35:54,599
everyone

976
00:35:55,360 --> 00:35:56,320
must die eventually.

977
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:57,840
It may be

978
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,239
heavier than Mount Tai.

979
00:35:59,679 --> 00:36:00,360
Want some fruit?

980
00:36:00,599 --> 00:36:02,519
What are you doing? What?

981
00:36:03,239 --> 00:36:04,159
Are you still watching that?

982
00:36:04,159 --> 00:36:05,039
I wasn't, I...

983
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,119
What are you hiding?

984
00:36:06,519 --> 00:36:07,599
Stop just barging in.

985
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,199
Can't you knock?

986
00:36:09,199 --> 00:36:10,320
I'm a grown man.

987
00:36:10,599 --> 00:36:11,760
I just want you to eat fruit.

988
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,880
Is it my fault now?

989
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:13,800
Get out.

990
00:36:15,719 --> 00:36:16,519
Eat the fruit.

991
00:36:17,079 --> 00:36:17,480
Grandma.

992
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:20,199
She meddles in everything.

993
00:36:20,239 --> 00:36:21,280
Won't let me watch comedies.

994
00:36:28,719 --> 00:36:29,280
Or

995
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:30,800
lighter than a feather.

996
00:36:32,039 --> 00:36:32,679
And I

997
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:35,000
am stuck in the middle.

998
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,719
Ancient times had Mencius' mother,

999
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,920
today has Xiaocan saving his mother.

1000
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:44,440
And this story

1001
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:46,519
will go down in history.

1002
00:36:47,239 --> 00:36:48,199
Are you still watching?
